channel.title: RetroScape - going out with a bang!
channel.description:
[center]RetroScape is a Server developed by me and only me. As from now i'm now accepting Staff Applicants, if you wish to apply fillout the format below. This [b]will[/b] be my last RuneScape Private Server so you can expect alot from this. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [b][u]Staff List[/u][/b] Server Developer(s); X Entinity X, Exion, Ix Soulcist xI Forum Developer(s); Jordan Cardwell Gfx Designer(s); Krackkid Model Developer(s); Reyx7 Server Administrator(s); Mss Destiny Server Moderator(s); Reyx7, RuneSpace Forum Administrator(s); X Entinity X, Exion, Jordan Cardwell Forum Moderator(s); Soft, Mimmel Skype team member(s); Mimmel Beta Tester(s); 6 Application Format, you must meet these standards to apply.
What are you applying for? How old are you? How long have you been coding Java? Do you code any other language except from Java? Why would you like to join? Do you have; msn, ventrio, email or skype? Any other information can be posted here (optional, it helps lots).
[/center] If you wish to see the Server in its Development stages please look here; http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,474546.0.html
